# Roadmap

## Phase 1: Platform Construction (Q1-Q2 2024)
- Architect core platform infrastructure.
- Integrate major blockchains including Ethereum and Binance Smart Chain.
- Develop basic automation for contract deployment.

## Phase 2: Beta Program (Q3 2024)
- Launch beta release with early adopters.
- Collect and implement user feedback.
- Introduce initial analytics dashboard.

## Phase 3: Expansion and Security (Q4 2024)
- Roll out advanced workflow automation.
- Complete comprehensive security audits.
- Expand blockchain support and integrations.

## Phase 4: Official Launch and Growth (Q1 2025)
- Release stable version publicly.
- Formalize partnerships and ecosystem collaborations.
- Provide documentation, training, and community support.

## Key Milestones
- Completion of MVP
- Beta release
- Security certification
- Partnership announcements

## Short-Term Goals
- Build a robust user base and provide excellent support.

## Long-Term Goals
- Establish LLM Studio as the leading automation platform for web3.

## Future Expansion
- Add AI-driven predictive analytics.
- Support decentralized governance modules.
- Expand to multiple languages and chains.